{"tid":2186797,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"騰訊以 14 億美元收購《戰甲神兵 Warframe》團隊的母公司樂遊科技","createTime":"2020-09-03T08:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T08:20:01.000Z","uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9f2de095ee0387ff81713d11aa41324a287763a6","tid":2186797,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:15:11.000Z","msg":"根據 InvestGame 報導，中國遊戲大廠騰訊透過旗下子公司意象架構投資（ Image Frame Investment），以 14 億美元價格收購了香港遊戲開發商與營運商樂遊科技。<br />\n<br />\n  樂遊科技旗下擁有玩家熟悉的《戰甲神兵（Warframe）》加拿大研發團隊 Digital Ext<br />\nremes、《核彈風雲（Dirty Bomb）》研發團隊 Splash Damage，樂遊科技也取得包括像是<br />\n《變形金剛》、《文明帝國》等 IP 授權來開發遊戲。<br />\n<br />\nInvestGame 報導指出，騰訊收購了樂遊科技後，樂遊科技將由騰訊全資擁有、並將撤回上<br />\n市的股份，而這筆交易還必須經相關當局同意等進行後續程序。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://investgame.net/news/tencent-has-acquired-leyou-technologies?rq=TENCENT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finvestgame.net%2Fnews%2Ftencent-has-acquired-leyou-technologies%3Frq%3DTENCENT&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hezsNYmc6RwURZU94nRINXI%3D&h=4618b8ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://investgame.net/news/tencent-has-acquired-leyou-technologies?rq=TENCENT</a>"},{"pid":"99881735217266a810856a16d025c24017b12d1c","tid":2186797,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:17:00.000Z","msg":"之前Beta開始玩 終於唔洗再玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91f0e49435373535a5bd76c2614b6ef0f7b3a57","tid":2186797,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:17:07.000Z","msg":"等睇騰訊被封殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c9e2bda2fb0c2705f01d5c6ca5354541312b6a","tid":2186797,"uid":70624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:17:25.000Z","msg":"神game要收皮了"},{"pid":"7e3f226dd7dd8151eb846d9919195e50a18b1734","tid":